{"tid":2499503,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男子被控不斷致電滋擾女警 今裁定罪名不成立","createTime":"2021-04-22T02:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T02:59:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c12c911b6571c6639cd879c55cfcc8416fecd85f","tid":2499503,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:37:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15186\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15186&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=ad79076e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15186</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第四庭<br />\n#王證瑜裁判官<br />\n#電話滋擾 #續審(2/2)<br />\n<br />\n👥吳(32)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：不斷打電話<br />\n[228章簡易治罪條例20(c)]<br />\n<br />\n(1)被控於今年5月27日在香港，無合理因由而不斷打電話給女偵緝警長55519，做成煩擾<br />\n<br />\n(2)被控於今年5月27日在香港，無合理因由而不斷打電話給女偵緝高級警員56170，做成煩擾<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n📌裁決速報： 兩項罪名不成立🎉"},{"pid":"c7feb92011434bb4ff15a5f75daa0aea602138d4","tid":2499503,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:42:00.000Z","msg":"合理"},{"pid":"5b9dd7af13f86a00b8652e349810c3b7a9281ea1","tid":2499503,"uid":292987,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:42:59.000Z","msg":"電話幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9b7110e2a7a0772885f4cd285851682c881d8e","tid":2499503,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:47:52.000Z","msg":"愛是最大權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f9a5bd805f3555040611f2c034cce3b46f5dd2","tid":2499503,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:52:11.000Z","msg":"王官指出本案主要爭議點為電話是否由被告打出，根據電訊商提供的用戶資料，雖實際用戶為被告吳啟鑫，但與被告同住的父親是登記用戶，電訊商報告亦於今年3月2日才開設，只顯示去年7月1日至今年7月1日的用戶資料，相關資料亦「可加可減」。另警方雖在被告床上搜出涉案電話號碼的電話卡，但搜屋時已是案發後3個月，其父親亦在場。王官認為雖然紀錄上被告為用戶，相當可疑，但仍未能在毫無疑點下證明案發當日由被告使用涉案號碼，故裁定被告罪名不成立。"},{"pid":"ed69bef51be759831f30242777a1ac38925df186","tid":2499503,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:54:31.000Z","msg":"人地追警女 者 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你個狗閪有人溝 汁到啦"},{"pid":"b4f856e645b7f2f596f9d0104b59dac4f0a237fb","tid":2499503,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:57:19.000Z","msg":"呢啲無聊案就要毫無疑點先判到, 社運大撚把疑點都入鳩你"},{"pid":"b3c6dc3d8a05b4e067e744ba8d6a2a0e7f84ea81","tid":2499503,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:59:07.000Z","msg":"屌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}